All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Address
An Address class is used to store the data of an address, dividing it into parts
Administrator
An Administrator class is used to allow administrators to access playgrounds and activate or delete any of them
AdminUI
AdminUI class allows the admins to interact with the system using the console
eWallet
A eWallet class is used to call an external service to transfer money between different users in the system
eWalletUI
eWalletUI class is used to enable users to access their eWallets and do operations on them
GoFoSystem
GoFoSystem class is used as the basis of the system, it stores all the users and admins' data and accesses the UI
Main  
Player
A Player class is an extension of the User class, adding properties and methods of the player
PlayerUI
PlayerUI class is used to enable players to interact with the system using the console
Playground
A Playground class is used to store playgrounds' data and the operations to be done on them
PlaygroundOwner
A PlaygroundOwner class is an extension of the User class, adding the properties and methods of the owner
PlaygroundOwnerUI
PlaygroundOwnerUI class is used to enable playground owners to interact with the system using the console
Team
A Team class is used to group players together into a team with an owner and team members
TimeSlot
A TimeSlot class is used to store a date and a starting hour and and ending hour to a specific time slot
UI
UI class is used to enable users and admins to interact with the system using the console, and direct them to other specific UI classes
User
A User class is an abstract class used to make generalization for Players and Playground Owners in the system.
